quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,37,"Markaasuu Aadam ka helay Rabbigiis ereyo uu ku ilhaamiyey{2}, wuuna ka toobad aqbalay. hubaal (Alle) waa Toobad Aqbalaha, Naxariista Badan.",footnotes:1:[. Alle wuxuu baray Aadam kelmedo lagu toobad dalbo uu ka aqbalay, waana kelmedaha ku soo arooray Suuradda Al- Acraaf Aayadda:],footnotes:2:[.]
  2,38,"Waxaanu nidhi: Ka dega xaggeeda (Jannada) dhammaantiin, markuu Xaggayga idiinka yimaado hanuun, qofkii raaca Hanuunkayga, cabsi ma ahaaneyso korkooda, mana murugoonayaan."
  2,39,"Kuwase gaalooba oo beeniya Aayadahayaga, waa iyaga ehlu-Naarka, gudaheeday ku dhex waari weligood."
